Voice of God

Simon Bovey, BBC Radio drama

In a remote region of Australia, Britain is developing the ultimate weapon. Their aim, a silent war, over before the enemy knows it has begun.  But according to Aboriginal dreamtime, it&#039;s Armageddon.
